matthew armsby the leopold leadership program skip to main content search this site the leopold leadership program about fellows news fellowship information resources login fellowships positions early career environmental scholars new fellowships new positions matthew armsby matthew armsby contact information early career fellow center for ocean solutions matthew armsby is an early career fellow with the center for ocean solutions cos where he focuses on the law and policy of us ocean governance since his arrival at cos he has focused on coastal and marine spatial planning as a platform for improving state and federal ocean governance on a number of fronts including providing for proactive and coordinated decisionmaking among policy makers and resource managers improving government transparency and accountability and supporting the development and use of the best available science and tools tags oceans & coasts 2012 leopold leadership program the stanford woods institute for the environment stanford university stanford ca 94305
